INSERT INTO `products_product` VALUES (1,'Royal Canin Maxi Adult Dry Dog Food','Royal Canin Maxi Adult Dry Dog Food is specially designed for large breed dogs (26-44kg), aged 15 months and older. This formula supports joint health, weight maintenance, and digestive wellness. Enriched with omega-3 fatty acids (EPA & DHA), it promotes healthy skin and a balanced diet for your large dog',190,'Royal Canin','Adult (1 - 7 Years)','0.220','https://i.ibb.co/mCWZYKd6/SHN24-MAXI-ADULT-DRY-PACKSHOT-B1-Med-Res-Basic-1083392-1200x1210.png',1,1,'2025-04-04 22:24:03.858000',6,1,1,''),(2,'Royal Canin Labrador Retriever Adult Dry Dog Food','Royal Canin Labrador Retriever Adult Dry Dog Food is designed for Labrador Retrievers aged 15 months and older. This formula supports healthy weight with adjusted calories, increased protein, and reduced fat. Enriched with omega-3 fatty acids (EPA & DHA), it promotes healthy skin, coat, and joints for active dogs.',2736,'Royal Canin','Adult (1 - 7 Years)','3','https://i.ibb.co/27drvcVF/royal-canin-labrador-retriever-adult-dry-dog-food-12-kg-1.webp',1,0,'2025-04-05 00:05:21.462000',2,1,1,''),(3,'Drools Powerbites Flavour Blueberries Pouch 135 Gm','Rich in protein with blueberry ﬂavour\nHealthy and nutritious dog treat\nContains No corn, No soya, No wheat\nIrresistible chewy dog treat made with Real Chicken\nHighly digestible treat',149,'Drools','All Age','0.135','https://i.ibb.co/chcn4fGf/71-Wh6-rtol-L-SL1500.jpg',1,1,'2025-04-06 00:25:23.466000',6,1,1,''),(4,'Pedigree Adult Chicken and Liver Chunks Wet Dog Food – 70g','Pedigree Adult Chicken & Liver Chunks Wet food in Gravy offers 100% complete and balanced nutrition. Made with high-quality ingredients, it provides essential nutrients to keep pets happy and healthy. It can be easily mixed with regular dry food or home-cooked meals for a delicious and nutritious meal.',539,'Pedigree','Adult (1 - 7 Years)','0.07','https://i.ibb.co/S4cpxFpT/61j-JZ0c-RWk-L-SL1000.webp',1,0,'2025-04-06 00:25:23.466000',6,1,1,''),(5,'Pedigree PRO Expert Nutrition Puppy Large Breed Dry Dog Food','Pedigree PRO Puppy large breed dog food provides your furry companion with the best possible nutrition for their growth and overall well-being. A premium and expertly formulated diet designed to meet the specific needs of your growing puppy (age 3-18 months). Developed in collaboration with veterinarians and nutritionists at the renowned Waltham Petcare Science Institute, this dog food offers superior nutrition for your dog’s optimal health and happiness.',3528,'Pedigree','Puppy (0 - 1 Years)','10','https://i.ibb.co/p6gCR5vb/PEDIGREE-PRO-Expert-Nutrition-Large-Breed-Puppy-Dry-Dog-Food-FOP-10kg-jpg-7-scaled.webp',1,0,'2025-04-06 00:25:23.466000',6,1,1,''),(6,'Barkbutler Boh The Bear – Squeaky & Plush Dog Toy','Barkbutler Boh the Bear is a plush dog toy that is durably stitched since it has an added layer of fabric to increase resistance and is made from super-soft polyester fabric. This dog toy has a squeaker inside that makes a squeaky noise every time your pet interacts with it by tugging on the toy. Interactive dog toys such as this allow your dog to chew, fetch tug, and bite on it while getting the right amount of exercise. This soft toy is ideal for x-small-medium dogs (0-20kg) of various breeds including dachshunds, spitz, pom, etc. This toy is strong but not indestructible and is best suited for pet dogs that have moderate chewing, cuddling, and indoor playing styles. Not recommended for aggressive chewers.',594,'BarkButler','All Age','','https://i.ibb.co/zVgNpYRK/Image-1.webp',1,1,'2025-04-06 00:25:23.466000',6,1,3,''),(8,'Drools Real Chicken & Chicken Liver Chunks in Gravy Wet Puppy Food – 150 g','Drools Real Chicken and Chicken Liver in gravy offer your puppy fresh and tasty wet food at every meal.This great-tasting puppy food contains a high-quality omega 3 fatty acid to support your puppies brain & eye development. This pack contains mouth-watering flavour, so you can give your puppy a balanced diet with delicious and healthy. Your pet will love the gravy, which provides all the nutrients to fulfil your pet needs for a healthy life.',540,'Drools','Puppy (0 - 1 Years)','0.15','https://i.ibb.co/ccbQ2tR0/Drools-Jack-Puppy-Chunks-In-Gravy-150-g-Front.webp',1,0,'2025-04-10 15:09:25.794000',6,1,1,''),(9,'Drools Adult Chicken Chunks in Gravy Wet Dog Food – 150 g','Drools Chicken Chunks in Gravy Wet Dog Food is a delectable meal that will satisfy your dog’s taste buds. This dog food is packed with vitamins to support overall health and a strong immune system. It also contains minerals that promote dental health. With a balanced diet and irresistible taste, this pack provides everything your dog needs for a healthy life.',365,'Drools','Adult (1 - 7 Years)','0.15','https://i.ibb.co/8n49KdrT/drool-chunk.webp',1,0,'2025-04-10 15:09:25.794000',6,1,1,''),(10,'Royal Canin Rottweiler Adult Dry Dog Food','Suitable for Rottweilers aged 18 months old and over, Royal Canin Rottweiler Adult is specially formulated with all the nutritional needs of your adult dog in mind. Royal Canin Rottweiler Adult Dry Dog Food contains specific nutrients – such as taurine, EPA, and DHA – that help to support healthy cardiac function. Royal Canin Rottweiler Adult Dry Dog Food also contributes to the maintenance of optimal muscle mass and ideal body weight, thanks to adapted protein content and the inclusion of L-Carnitine. This diet – rationed appropriately to regulate proper food intake – should be fed in conjunction with an effective exercise routine. Whether working or just on a walk with its owner, the Rottweiler is always active and enthusiastic, which means it requires nutrients that support the health of its joints and bones. This is the reason Royal Canin® Rottweiler Adult has been enriched with EPA and DHA – these omega-3 fatty acids help to support your dog’s healthy bones and joints. What’s more, the exclusive kibble in Royal Canin® Rottweiler Adult is specially designed to make it easier for your dog to pick up, it also encourages it to chew more thoroughly to help increase the feeling of fullness and maintain an ideal weight.',3069,'Royal Canin','Adult (1 - 7 Years)','3','https://i.ibb.co/wF9bR9C5/royal-canin-rottweiler-adult-dry-dog-food-12-kg-1.webp',1,0,'2025-04-10 15:09:25.794000',11,1,1,''),(11,'Royal Canin Mini Starter Dry Dog Food','From a nutritional perspective, it’s very important that your mini-breed dogs and their young pups eat food that’s specifically tailored to their unique nutritional requirements. That’s why Royal Canin Mini Starter Dry Dog Food provides everything needed for dogs weighing up to 10kg as well as for its weaning puppies up to 2 months old. ROYAL CANIN Mini Starter Mother & Babydog is designed using ROYAL CANIN’s ‘Start Complex’ – an exclusive combination of nutritional elements the same as those in the mother’s milk – reinforced with specific nutrients that contribute to supporting the puppies’ digestive health and natural defenses. The nutritional profile of ROYAL CANIN Mini Starter Mother & Babydog is adapted to the mother’s high energy requirements at the critical period during the end of gestation and the beginning of lactation. The kibble is also easy to rehydrate to a porridge-like consistency; essentially by soaking the kibble. This consistency is not only very palatable for the mother but also facilitates the puppies’ transition from their mother’s milk to more solid food in order to wean them effectively.',1330,'Royal Canin','Puppy (0 - 1 Years)','1','https://i.ibb.co/gMry7LWG/royal-canin-mini-starter-dry-dog-food-1-kg.webp',1,0,'2025-04-10 15:09:25.794000',7,1,1,''),(12,'Himalaya Erina EP Shampoo','Prevents ectoparasites: Erina EP controls ectoparasites (external parasites) like ticks, fleas and lice in pets. Controls skin infections: Its antimicrobial and antifungal actions, prevent skin infections and improves the overall condition of the skin.',575,'Himalaya','All Age','0.45','